data.description: Looking to move? This beautiful home is located in South College Station in Woodland Hills. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a study, walk in pantry, drop zone and oversize garage, this home sits on a cul-de-sac and has no rear neighbors. Open and split floorplan with modern touches and a ton of natural light. The primary suite has plenty of room for oversized furniture. Large backyard with covered patio and tons of trees. Close to shopping, restaurants and on the hospital grid (never lost power during the "2021 Big Freeze"). Come see if this home is what you have been looking for!
